{
  "stem": "21004.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the house was not-- it was very a poor house, because one room, we had a big room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we had a foyer and we had also another big room for storage for food, and then a cellar for milk and all that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had two cows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had chickens, everything what we need so we could live quietly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had two brothers, two sisters, two older sisters and two older brothers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My older sister was Sarah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was born 1908.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My other sister, the second sister, was Perl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was born 1909.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then my brother, my older brother, was born 1912.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My second brother was born 1914.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was born 1915 in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was the youngest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was very young and they were older, much older for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had always good relations, because we had to respect our mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have no father, so she was the father and the mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So always you were very respectable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mother was very religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also my grandfather was very religious, so you have to respect.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was really not to do things, nothing wrong, just everything has to be right, not to disturb the mother, not to get her nervous.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had a discipline by ourself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You made [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was a very good mother, Nice looking, beautiful lady.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got a picture from my-- my mother and father when she sent-- when she got married, she sent to the United States to my aunt and uncles.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I found it here after 1949 when I came here and found those pictures what my aunt gave me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All the pictures from my grandma I got pictures, and cousins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean we were Orthodox Jews, not really fanatic.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
